premise_source_doc_sentence: In June 2006 the band released an EP , Tales Told by Dead Friends , which they sold to people by following the 2006 edition of Warped Tour and offering copies ; it eventually sold 10,000 copies .
Kusabi sold 10,917 copies in its second week , 3,442 copies in its third week and 1,832 copies in its fourth week .
Selling 10 copies per day is expected to eventually let the sellers exceed the minimum wage by 40 percent .

The bonus material on disc 3 was recorded at Acid Mothers Temple from 1995 to 1996 and originally released on Acid Mother 's Temple & The Melting Paraiso U.F.O. , a cassette issued in 1996 in a limited edition of 10 copies .
It is sold for 100 pesos , half of which the seller keeps .
